    SNAP-ChIP<sup>®</sup> spike-in control panels to validate specificity. The goal of this
    partnership is to create a portfolio of SNAP-ChIP<sup>®</sup> validated histone PTM
    antibodies; providing researchers a new level of confidence in the data they
    generate by creating a new standard for specificity in ChIP antibody
    validation.
